headline: AutoZone to Release Fourth Quarter Fiscal 2025 Earnings September 23, 2025
summary: MEMPHIS, Tenn., Aug. 20, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- AutoZone, Inc. (NYSE: AZO), the leading retailer and distributor of automotive replacement parts and accessories in the Americas, will release results for its fourth quarter ended Saturday, August 30, 2025, before market open on Tuesday, September 23, 2025.
